/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd62d353e1834fe81cfead696c2b22a10e35cf0","tid":256810,"uid":75457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:57:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>btec係比啲冇5條2既人入，認受性一定差過asso/hd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最低係33222</blockquote><br />\n你以為asso真係比5條2入？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入面大部份都係19-25分既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8501e644ddd314a9098f44e856c267af70d105","tid":256810,"uid":44113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:57:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>btec係比啲冇5條2既人入，認受性一定差過asso/hd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最低係33222</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cbcc.edu.hk/chi/programmes/fulltime/hm/btec.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbcc.edu.hk%2Fchi%2Fprogrammes%2Ffulltime%2Fhm%2Fbtec.html&d=wXXh3%2FvEyoclwUBZuqJaJBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=a952c6d2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cbcc.edu.hk/chi/programmes/fulltime/hm/btec.html</a><br />\n只要有一科3就得啦喎，前年去in，佢話我maths同ls有4係佢地到已經好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁5，5星，5星星叫乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係我認真咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁有5有5* 唔使讀呢啲啦<br />\n搵黎比....<br />\n我都知香港係鐘意見高拜 見低踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02907dfbe1d839fa6d095cd23b1152d46fe938f3","tid":256810,"uid":44113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:59:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>btec係比啲冇5條2既人入，認受性一定差過asso/hd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\