都要有一定gpa<br />\n同btec lv5一樣 有merit 即係gpa2.7-3<br />\n都好大機會入到sf degree <br />\nDistinct 多 加ielts高分都有人入返ugc <br />\n都係果句本身讀既人程度低 自然少啲人入到ugc <br />\n如果相同實力 去btec 一定好過ive <br />\n起碼無exam先 如果讀business<br />\nAsso唔敢講 本地升學為主有少少優勢<br />\n但有心讀兩者唔會好似上面講到差咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d890df8a38d0810836f270404c5fa8850debf195","tid":256810,"uid":44113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:18:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>總之本地btec唔抵讀,asso/hd仲好啦</blockquote><br />\n咁樣結論對我呢啲畢左業好唔公平<br />\n睇野唔係咁睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a4b7f74173f7982f253b95439d9a4d95c6272e","tid":256810,"uid":90801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:25:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>btec係比啲冇5條2既人入，認受性一定差過asso/hd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最低係33222</blockquote><br />\n你以為asso真係比5條2入？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入面大部份都係19-25分既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係度嚇9人<br />\n21分up 都好難搵到啦（講緊3322喎）<br />\n痴線 擾敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀緊果陣全部高分都係呢堆人 <br />\n根本冇得同佢地鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申18分 asso升hku"},{"pid":"884378859ed003aed7be03a9d3f1f64966babf05","tid":256810,"uid":75457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:35:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cbcc.edu.hk/chi/programmes/fulltime/hm/btec.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbcc.edu.hk%2Fchi%2Fprogrammes%2Ffulltime%2Fhm%2Fbtec.html&d=wXXh3%2FvEyoclwUBZuqJaJBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=a952c6d2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cbcc.edu.hk/chi/programmes/fulltime/hm/btec.html</a><br />\n只要有一科3就得啦喎，前年去in，佢話我maths同ls有4係佢地到已經好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁5，5星，5星星叫乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係我認真咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁有5有5* 唔使讀呢啲啦<br />\n搵黎比....<br />\n我都知香港係鐘意見高拜 見低踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇話見高拜 見低踩，但一定衰過 hd/ asso</blockquote><br />\n只可以講sample pool無咁大<br />\n同埋普遍讀既人差啲姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讀書差都想有重生機會</blockquote><br />\n如果中英有2，同埋其他科都2以上，一定係hd/asso先，btec通常比你外國升學為主，asso/hd係本地升學為主</blockquote><br />\n而家香港本地top up 都會收<br />\n果陣有幾個都入左scope 但佢地英文ok ielts 考到6.5<br />\nUgc我識既既話有一個 細我一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 學霸黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老實講,space,ive,cccu,hkcc grad到已經入到scope/cdp,冇ielts要求，ugc大約有3已經有offer,gpa再好啲已經有三大ugc offer</blockquote><br />\n臨訓前覆埋你<br />\nGrad到都要有一定gpa<br />\n同btec lv5一樣 有merit 即係gpa2.7-3<br />\n都好大機會入到sf degree <br />\nDistinct 多 加ielts高分都有人入返ugc <br />\n都係果句本身讀既人程度低 自然少啲人入到ugc <br />\n如果相同實力 去btec 一定好過ive <br />\n起碼無exam先 如果讀business<br />\nAsso唔敢講 本地升學為主有少少優勢<br />\n但有心讀兩者唔會好似上面講到差咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你可以望下space,hkcc,cccu個啲升學率幾多先，基本上唔介意讀差少少既sf degree例如scope,cdp既話，升學率可以100%，雖然辛苦啲，但認受性或者名氣高啲，本地僱主你會覺得識hd/asso多啲定btec多啲，調番轉係外國就業就相反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係話btec唔好，如果外國就業又唔想讀degree就btec好啲，但本地升學/就業一定hd/asso好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8462c868196826d1149fcd34a3d5fcfc029ba60a","tid":256810,"uid":37874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:43:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><bl